entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Nien Nunb is grateful for your help.
entries.journal_entry_description: Help Nien Nunb by recovering some parts for his linguistic decoder and by getting rid of a bounty hunter who is pursuing a personal vendetta against him.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Recover the parts Nien needs for his linguistic decoder from the Canyon Corsairs.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Track down and eliminate a bounty hunter that is after Nien. His last known location was a small village south of Nym's stronghold.
